descriptionHTML:
The watch face is inspired by Suprematism art movement and Ivan Kliun painter. Watch face‘s design is simple and refers to an abstract art based upon "the supremacy of pure artistic feeling".

FEATURES
For art lovers: simple abstract art design, inspired by Suprematism art movement
Supports rectangle and round Android Wear™ watches
Supports low-power Ambient Mode for extended battery life
Unisex: for boys and girls ;)

COMPATIBILITY
The watch face is compatible with the following Android Wear™ watches:
● Motorola Moto 360
● LG G Watch
● LG G Watch R
● LG Watch Urban
● Samsung Gear Live
● Sony SmartWatch 3
● ASUS ZenWatch

CREDITS
Designed by Polina Kusnezova
Created by Valeri Ilyin
